ttp://pub73.ezboard.com/uwazuzubalu.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Wazu Zubalu</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Tavern Regular</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(8/14/01 7:35:08 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: PvP Question: How do I beat....</span><hr size=1> Anything is possible given the right conditions, but your chances of beating a necro around your level with full hp and mana are slim to none unless the necro really sucks.<br>
<br>
People can drone on and on about the right 'tactics' to use when fighting a necro solo, but if the necro is any good at all, the end result will probably be the same.<br>
<br>
My advice is to stay grouped, and travel with friends.  (Preferably healer friends.)  Once you hit the high levels things will swing more in your favor, and you'll be able to send the necros gating a lot more often. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=FAEBD7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub73.ezboard.com/usilverygold.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Silvery Gold</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>poon</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(8/14/01 7:37:42 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: PvP Question: How do I beat....</span><hr size=1> Thanks, Wazu... I appreciate the advice. <br>
