<br>
Basically, if you can't escape and the person you're against is at the same speed you are, with a decent MR you can kill the necro pet and just suck it up while you get nuked/dot'd up, then if you can manage to kill the pet in time chase after the necro and they're screwed if they didn't land darkness on you because they can't stop to cast.  As for a mage, if they have a brain they'll gate before their pet dies and you'll live. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=FAEBD7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub73.ezboard.com/bsullonzektavern.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=firble>Firble</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>poon</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(8/15/01 2:09:24 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> I cant believe no ones suggested this...</span><hr size=1> But then again I am the best necro of all time, and know every possible little detail there is to know about them.<br>
